<section data-label="29 Onze aanpak">
  <div class="slide-frame">
    <div class="eyebrow">Onze aanpak</div>
    <h2 class="title" style="margin-top: 28px;">Drie pijlers. Eén traject.</h2>
    <p class="body" style="margin-top: 32px; max-width: 1300px;">
      Inzicht, kennis en een platform. Zo word je niet alleen AI-ready, maar AI-native.
    </p>

    <div style="margin-top: 72px; display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 28px; flex: 1; align-items: stretch;">

      <!-- Pillar 1 — SmartScan -->
      <div style="--c: #0891b2; background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--c) 28%, var(--border-soft)); border-radius: 20px; padding: 40px; display: flex; flex-direction: column;">
        <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 18px;">
          <div style="width: 56px; height: 56px; border-radius: 14px; background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--c) 12%, transparent); border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--c) 30%, transparent); color: var(--c); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0;">
            <svg width="30" height="30" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="7"/><path d="m21 21-4.3-4.3"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--ink-4);">01</span>
        </div>
        <h3 style="font-size: 42px; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 28px; letter-spacing: -0.02em; color: var(--c);">SmartScan</h3>
        <p style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--ink-2); margin-top: 12px;">Het inzicht.</p>
        <p style="font-size: 27px; line-height: 1.5; color: var(--ink-3); margin-top: 40px;">
          Snel inzicht in wat AI voor jouw bedrijf kan betekenen. Hoe AI-ready, of zelfs AI-native, ben je vandaag?
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Pillar 2 — Training -->
      <div style="--c: #B45309; background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--c) 28%, var(--border-soft)); border-radius: 20px; padding: 40px; display: flex; flex-direction: column;">
        <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 18px;">
          <div style="width: 56px; height: 56px; border-radius: 14px; background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--c) 12%, transparent); border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--c) 30%, transparent); color: var(--c); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0;">
            <svg width="30" height="30" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 10v6M2 10l10-5 10 5-10 5z"/><path d="M6 12v5c3 3 9 3 12 0v-5"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--ink-4);">02</span>
        </div>
        <h3 style="font-size: 42px; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 28px; letter-spacing: -0.02em; color: var(--c);">Training</h3>
        <p style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--ink-2); margin-top: 12px;">De kennis.</p>
        <p style="font-size: 27px; line-height: 1.5; color: var(--ink-3); margin-top: 40px;">
          Leer de mogelijkheden, bouw vertrouwen op in het gebruik van AI, en begrijp wat er onder de motorkap gebeurt.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Pillar 3 — SmartSpace -->
      <div style="--c: var(--accent-smartspace); background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--c) 28%, var(--border-soft)); border-radius: 20px; padding: 40px; display: flex; flex-direction: column;">
        <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 18px;">
          <div style="width: 56px; height: 56px; border-radius: 14px; background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--c) 12%, transparent); border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--c) 30%, transparent); color: var(--c); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0;">
            <svg width="30" height="30" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/><circle cx="4" cy="4" r="1.5"/><circle cx="20" cy="4" r="1.5"/><circle cx="4" cy="20" r="1.5"/><circle cx="20" cy="20" r="1.5"/><line x1="5.4" y1="5.4" x2="9.9" y2="9.9"/><line x1="18.6" y1="5.4" x2="14.1" y2="9.9"/><line x1="5.4" y1="18.6" x2="9.9" y2="14.1"/><line x1="18.6" y1="18.6" x2="14.1" y2="14.1"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--ink-4);">03</span>
        </div>
        <h3 style="font-size: 42px; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 28px; letter-spacing: -0.02em; color: var(--c);">SmartSpace</h3>
        <p style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--ink-2); margin-top: 12px;">Het platform.</p>
        <p style="font-size: 27px; line-height: 1.5; color: var(--ink-3); margin-top: 40px;">
          One-stop-shop met apps geënt op jouw bedrijf. Ze werken samen en vormen zo jouw eigen AI-platform.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="chrome">
      <div class="sa-brand"><img src="assets/logo.svg" alt="">Smart<span class="accent">Agents</span></div>
      <div>29 / 32</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
